<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.214603>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1, 2. Andidrilus nonuya sp. nov. 1 A. Clitellar region, ventral view. 1 B. Clitellum, lateral view. 2 A. C ommon seta. 2 B. Genital seta; right: complete; left: distal tip." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/214603/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.214604>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Andiodrilus nonuya sp. nov. A. Calciferous gland from segments 8 (top) and 9 (bottom) showing the external shape with lamellar structure. B. Nephridium of segment 20. C. Spermatheca of 6 / 7, 7 / 8, 8 / 9 (from top to bottom)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/214604/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

